      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span><strong> </strong>the <strong>wholegrain</strong> <strong>mustard</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining wholegrain mustard for another recipe!</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and whisk together – this is your <strong>mustard vinaigrette</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong> with the <strong>truffle oil </strong>in a separate bowl <strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> truffle mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
